<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 02:11:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 的比特币承诺在经济低迷时期兑现了现实</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-30/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-promise-meets-reality-during-downturn</link><description>战略的融资飞轮已断裂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNbgIOgYPiRA/v7/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-30/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-promise-meets-reality-during-downturn</guid></item><item><title>策略抛售加剧焦虑，比特币跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-30/bitcoin-slides-below-60-000-as-strategy-selloff-refuels-anxiety</link><description>周二，比特币暴跌 3.5%，跌至 58,000 美元，原因是投资者推翻了对 Strategy Inc. Michael Saylor 融资改革的初步信任投票，引发了人们对加密货币最大买家之一可能不再是持续需求来源的新担忧。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVwKogDxx6Ps/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2026 17:24:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-30/bitcoin-slides-below-60-000-as-strategy-selloff-refuels-anxiety</guid></item><item><title>策略可能会在融资模式改革中出售更多比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/strategy-says-it-may-sell-up-to-1-25-billlion-of-bitcoin</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 公布了对其比特币战略基础的融资模式的彻底改革，赋予自己更广泛的权力来出售加密货币、回购证券和保持流动性，以适应多年来积极积累的结构所承受的越来越大的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifEH6z6pWrqE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 12:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/strategy-says-it-may-sell-up-to-1-25-billlion-of-bitcoin</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的机构买家在比特币的双重打击下撤退</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/bitcoin-btc-etfs-face-record-4-billion-in-june-outflows-worst-since-launch</link><description>与此同时，比特币最大的机构需求来源正在动摇，随着交易所交易基金投资者以创纪录的速度撤资，以及对其最大企业买家背后的融资策略持续存在疑问，比特币日益面临风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipx2T93hKbqU/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 08:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/bitcoin-btc-etfs-face-record-4-billion-in-june-outflows-worst-since-launch</guid></item></channel></rss>